    <item>
      <title>Version 1.0.4 (104)</title>
      <link>https://www.contextmcp.app/</link>
      <sparkle:version>104</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.0.4</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>15.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Fix crash due to partial initialization of StdioTransport (<a rel="noopener" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/indragiek/Context/commit/ec0e9886be179cc3bb00eb56d0e95d7f2d2d8ad7">ec0e988</a>)</li>
<li>Fix broken handling of legacy SSE transport (<a rel="noopener" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/indragiek/Context/commit/4bac2d6405270ac7cb1f9b9d95204156db8f6410">4bac2d6</a>)</li>
<li>Build a universal binary for Intel and Apple Silicon (<a rel="noopener" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/indragiek/Context/commit/0528f8e36b2ae5372b062d69d6299bc28661469b">0528f8e</a>)</li>
<li>Use shared browser session for OAuth (<a rel="noopener" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/indragiek/Context/commit/ec26845e34f6044e5d8000793bc4fa4f5a2abaf5">ec26845</a>)</li>
<li>Allow HTTP connections for OAuth on localhost (<a rel="noopener" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/indragiek/Context/commit/f57c01f0ba7744c6911efcaedc07e5aead5d9863">f57c01f</a>)</li>
<li>Use stats.store for Sparkle analytics (<a rel="noopener" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/indragiek/Context/commit/c67fca33a8bc1e1458ad55c89de646d0a4221779">c67fca3</a>)</li>
<li>Fix $PATH resolution to use shell $PATH (<a rel="noopener" target="_blank" href="https://github.com/indragiek/Context/commit/ff896cf595159eae7a34717bc59e8a80039d9054">ff896cf</a>)</li>
</ul>
]]></description>
